{"tid":462481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又有！帶病開工　疑過度操勞病發猝死","createTime":"2017-11-08T14:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T16:21:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7a4c94968a6cb83056e2218f8c85e2f7922000","tid":462481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"今晨8時許，途人發現九龍灣宏基街5號對開，一輛的士違例停泊在中線，好奇心走近查看，發覺司機似昏迷車內，慌忙報警求助。警方及救護員接報到場，證實司機已氣絕身亡。該將屍體移往路旁，並用帳篷掩蓋，隨即展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n其後，警方根據資料追查，證實「的哥」姓陳（50歲），立即通知其家人到場協助。當陳妻攜同10歲兒子趕抵現場認屍時，母子哭得死去活來，需由女警在旁攙扶安慰。據悉，死者生前有病患紀錄，身上懷有藥物。警方不排除他因工作操勞，導致病發猝死，但死因仍有待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171108/bkn-20171108085157434-1108_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171108%2Fbkn-20171108085157434-1108_00822_001.html&d=AB%2BcY2C%2FDevFsiJ4lyasjf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b5f7fb17\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171108/bkn-20171108085157434-1108_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b277b90c46f44f774727b98e185cca088aa8a4d6","tid":462481,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:55:22.000Z","msg":"返工=死路"},{"pid":"f5cbe72c002a03d33fb7bc57a37355ea27053194","tid":462481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:56:01.000Z","msg":"不排除他因工作操勞，導致病發猝死<br />\n不排除他因工作操勞，導致病發猝死<br />\n不排除他因工作操勞，導致病發猝死"},{"pid":"28ff61ab78613b126e48e58a9292ca3e890e2e65","tid":462481,"uid":71726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"返工太危險了"},{"pid":"505b07c98c5379c83f80c137b4965c4fa9b6645c","tid":462481,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:06:06.000Z","msg":"老貓咪危言聳聽"},{"pid":"2bdab6f7ed112f1602cffbdbfb8733c946a08b4b","tid":462481,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"豬"},{"pid":"2a504839ad2e6eefd3b3d8a4003a919c79